name: Glyphs of Aegis
automation:
  - type: counter
    counter: Charged Essence Runes
    amount: lastCounterRequestedAmount
    allowOverflow: false
    errorBehaviour: raise
  - type: variable
    name: amt
    value: lastCounterRequestedAmount
  - type: counter
    counter: Inert Essence Runes
    amount: -amt
    allowOverflow: false
    errorBehaviour: warn
    fixedValue: true
  - type: condition
    condition: not targets
    onTrue:
      - type: roll
        dice: "{amt}d6"
        name: damred
        hidden: false
        displayName: Damage Reduced
      - type: variable
        name: origdam
        value: choice
        onError: "0"
      - type: condition
        condition: origdam > damred
        onTrue:
          - type: variable
            name: red
            value: damred
        onFalse:
          - type: variable
            name: red
            value: origdam
        errorBehaviour: "false"
      - type: target
        target: self
        effects:
          - type: damage
            damage: -{red}
            overheal: false
      - type: text
        text: >-
          Starting at 1st level, you can release the stored arcane power within your
          runes to absorb or deflect threatening attacks. Whenever you take
          damage, you can expend any number of charged runes as a reaction. Roll
          a number of d6s equal to the number of runes you expended, and reduce
          the damage by the total.


          When you reach 6th level, you can touch a creature as an action and expend up to 3 charged runes to transfer your protective power to it for up to 1 hour. The next time that creature takes damage within the next hour, it rolls 1d6 per charged rune spent and reduces the damage by the total. You canâ€™t transfer this power to a creature already under the effect of Glyph of Aegis.


          Your Glyph of Aegis die becomes a d8 at 14th level.


          Specify `-choice` for the amount of damage taken and `-amt` for number of runes you wish to spend.
        title: Effect
    onFalse:
      - type: condition
        condition: amt < 2
        onTrue:
          - type: condition
            condition: SorcererLevel < 14
            onTrue:
              - type: target
                target: all
                effects:
                  - type: ieffect2
                    name: ""
                    duration: null
                    effects: null
